<main id="content" class="content"> <header> <h1 class="title">The Twelfth Sunday After Pentecost</h1>
 <p class="subtitle" role="doc-subtitle">Jan 13, 2015 00:00</p>
</header> <p>
Loving God,
</p>

 <p>
Apathy is a vice <br></br>
easily disguised <br></br>
behind veils <br></br>
of busy lives, <br></br>
carefully built <br></br>
to avoid the <br></br>
demands of love.
</p>

 <p>
Forgive me, <br></br>
not just because <br></br>
I pretend to care, <br></br>
but that I <br></br>
deceive myself - <br></br>
believing in <br></br>
the pretending <br></br>
more than <br></br>
in the caring.
</p>

 <p>
 <i>Amen</i>
</p>




